"title": "8340: self-respect",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8340: self-respect",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>A sense of personal worth and dignity. Scripture points to the need for believers to ground their self-respect in God himself, rather than trusting in the opinion and valuation of other individuals or society as a whole.</p>\n<h2>Self-respect is often assumed</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:39\">MAT 22:39</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:31\">MRK 12:31</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:12\">MAT 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:19\">MAT 19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:3\">ROM 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:29\">EPH 5:29</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those who had self-respect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job12:3\">JOB 12:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job10:16\">JOB 10:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:25\">PRO 31:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:4\">PHP 3:4</a></p>\n<h2>The basis of self-respect</h2>\n<h3>A relationship with God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:13-Ps139:14\">PSA 139:13–139:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:6\">PSA 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:16-1Cor3:17\">1CO 3:16–3:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:12-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:12–6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:22\">EPH 2:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:4\">1TI 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>Equality in God's community</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:9-Jas1:10\">JAS 1:9–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:22-1Cor12:25\">1CO 12:22–12:25</a></p>\n<h3>A clear conscience and faithfulness to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:12\">2CO 1:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:18\">JHN 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:4\">GAL 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:18\">HEB 13:18</a></p>\n<h2>God's strength is a source of self-respect</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:19\">DAN 10:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:2\">EXO 15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam22:33\">2SA 22:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:5\">PSA 71:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:17\">PSA 89:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps118:14\">PSA 118:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:17\">2TI 4:17</a></p>\n<h2>Self-respect results from disciplined living</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job4:6\">JOB 4:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:3\">PRO 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:4\">1TH 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:2\">TIT 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Self-respect can be lost through humiliation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:19\">JER 31:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam10:1-2Sam10:5\">2SA 10:1–10:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr19:1-1Chr19:5\">1CH 19:1–19:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:1-2Sam13:22\">2SA 13:1–13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:33\">DAN 4:33</a></p>\n<h2>Self-respect can rest on wrong foundations</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:3\">GAL 6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:17-Deut8:18\">DEU 8:17–8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job20:6-Job20:7\">JOB 20:6–20:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:4-Phil3:7\">PHP 3:4–3:7</a></p>\n<h2>Ways in which self-respect can be undermined</h2>\n<h3>By others</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job30:1-Job30:15\">JOB 30:1–30:15</a></p>\n<h3>By the effects of sin and the work of Satan</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:2-Mark5:5\">MRK 5:2–5:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:27-Luke8:29\">LUK 8:27–8:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:25-Mark5:28\">MRK 5:25–5:28</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt9:20-Matt9:22\">MAT 9:20–9:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:43-Luke8:48\">LUK 8:43–8:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:13-Luke15:16\">LUK 15:13–15:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:12-Luke17:13\">LUK 17:12–17:13</a></p>\n<h3>By unwise spiritual zeal</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1\">GAL 6:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim5:1-1Tim5:2\">1TI 5:1–5:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:22\">JUD 1:22</a></p>",
